overview:

E-mail

A revolutionary way to charter yachts!

YachtsPanic.com is changing the way chartering yachts. Search, Compare, Read user reviews and Book OnLine! If you search for yacht charters in Greece (soon in Croatia and Turkey), then you are in the correct place.

We offer a selection of Sailing, Motor and Motor sailer yachts, all listed by their name, exclusive descriptions and specifications, photos, availability and tariffs.

Even same types, length, make, year and model yachts have differences which consist in equipment, treatment, maintenance and the way of the charterer is served and handled upon embarking and disembarking.

You are not just renting a car which may easily be replaced. While chartering a yacht, you need to secure a memorable and safe vacation!

YachtsPanic.com registered operators, owners and brokers, offer distinguished services.

YachtsPanic.com takes every possible effort to maintain and secure a high level of services by verifying each one of the operators behind every listed yacht. Additionally, a second verification is commenced by PayPal™, while creating a business account and increasing transactions limits.

Our reputation and proper functionality is based on cooperation with reputable, leading and trust worthy charter brokers and individual yacht owners. Most of them are members of SITESAP or HYBA, the two leading yacht owners and brokers associations in Greece.
